article.description: — Jameer Nelson Jr. scored 19 points as Delaware easily beat Siena 83-63 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Nelson Jr., Painter lead Delaware past Siena 83-63
article.linkText: Nelson Jr., Painter lead Delaware past Siena 83-63
article.story: ALBANY, N.Y. -- — Jameer Nelson Jr. scored 19 points as Delaware easily beat Siena 83-63 on Saturday night. Dylan Painter added 16 points and 10 rebounds for Delaware (1-1). Ryan Allen chipped in 15 points. Andrew Carr had seven rebounds and three blocks for the Fightin’ Blue Hens. Colby Rogers had 20 points for the Saints (0-2). Anthony Gaines had eight points and 10 rebounds.
